# Superwikia_Documentation_Library
================================

The **Superwikia Documentation Library** is the collective infrastructure of the _Superwikia Alpha Codebase_. It contains the native transcribe and commands for accessing the _S-Terminal_ and all descendant consoles.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
